item.title: Git
item.description: This page provides an overview of different techniques and skill levels related to Git, including basic, intermediate, and advanced techniques. Basic These are the basic skills, helpful even for beginning courses and activities. Intermediate These would be considered intermediate skills, applied in higher-level courses and activities. Advanced These are advanced skills, useful for more experienced users and advanced projects.
